{"tid":1323241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【沙田衝突】涉咬斷警手指　被控傷人襲警　港大畢業生提堂獲保釋","createTime":"2019-07-16T07:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T03:18:40.000Z","uid":279159,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"53040f20c7a7cafa50d92511b7af190166e2d755","tid":1323241,"uid":279159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:31:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/沙田衝突-港大畢業生涉咬斷警手指-案件今提堂/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%B6%89%E5%92%AC%E6%96%B7%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%87-%E6%A1%88%E4%BB%B6%E4%BB%8A%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82%2F&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=6381c3ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%B6%89%E5%92%AC%E6%96%B7%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%87-%E6%A1%88%E4%BB%B6%E4%BB%8A%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82%2F&h=6c31bff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/沙田衝突-港大畢業生涉咬斷警手指-案件今提堂/</a><br />\n<br />\n沙田大遊行後新城市廣場爆發警民衝突，一名警員右手無名指一截遭咬斷。一名港大應屆畢業生、22 歲姓杜的男子，暫控兩項蓄意傷人、一項襲警及一項未能在規定下出示身份證明文件罪，案件今日下午在沙田裁判法院提堂，被告獲准保釋，保釋金1萬元，另需1萬元人事擔保。<br />\n<br />\n早前《蘋果日報》經比對現場照片和片段後，質疑涉案男子曾經被警員挖眼，而連登討論區有網民比對，認為疑似挖眼警員與手指受傷警員的服飾、鞋子相似，懷疑兩者均為同一警員。<br />\n<br />\n相片可見當時警員手指位置在示威者眼及口部。不過香港 01 早前引述一名不具名的人士指，警長「插眼」說法是虛假。"},{"pid":"58141a0de820bba407e72735b58b9eef003e257d","tid":1323241,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:33:11.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有人冒警！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n推post時幫手廣傳有人冒警！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被動變主動</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"82c6100bb2d123c944da2554dd8e0f372bd1840c","tid":1323241,"uid":107216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:33:11.000Z","msg":"香港01就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721cc8943ebb26a47cf8a89273c4a271e18b7227","tid":1323241,"uid":9726,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:44:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"815313b957aa29150c36f7ce5a3adbd29ea63161","tid":1323241,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"一名不具名的人士<br />\n有消費指<br />\n傳<br />\n<br />\n新聞嚟架？<br />\n有消息指你老母就死呀"},{"pid":"e19d3dcc3ac1dc1a7d010bc23c9c76135fd2e100","tid":1323241,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c722c676139a1800636054b08cf9f06e04d45267","tid":1323241,"uid":7763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"815313b957aa29150c36f7ce5a3adbd29ea63161","tid":1323241,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"一名不具名的人士<br />\n有消費指<br />\n傳<br />\n<br />\n新聞嚟架？<br />\n有消息指你老母就死呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:48:25.000Z","msg":"因為佢地confirm唔到"},{"pid":"6844573612cfeb1daf05341ab37d2811b41db262","tid":1323241,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:18:40.000Z","msg":"慘被挖眼 未落口供就提堂<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1325709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1325709</a>"}]}